  "title": "Alien Evolution: First-person Model",
  "description": "A compatibility bridge mod designed to make First-person Model & Alien Evolution work perfectly together",
  "body": "<!-- Top banner/divider (centered) -->\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1283693/description_4d7ce501-4ea4-4e42-a5b8-cfd68c7adcec.png\" width=\"850\" alt=\"\">\n</p>\n\n<!-- ICONS: rock-solid centering via table -->\n<table align=\"center\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"margin:0 auto;border-collapse:collapse;\">\n  <tr>\n    <td style=\"padding:0 12px; text-align:center;\">\n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/alien-evolution-first-person-model\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n        <img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1283693/description_32d76132-c575-49a8-84c0-c61d82fd4206.png\" width=\"75\" height=\"75\" alt=\"Modrinth\">\n      </a>\n    </td>\n    <td style=\"padding:0 12px; text-align:center;\">\n      <a href=\"https://discord.gg/7yFQGexMn8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">\n        <img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1283693/description_36d6235e-d79c-46a2-b176-33fc481d3870.png\" width=\"75\" height=\"75\" alt=\"Discord\">\n      </a>\n    </td>\n    <td style=\"padding:0 12px; text-align:center;\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/alien-evolution-first-person-model\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">\n        <img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1283693/description_bb63ba1d-5f20-4c53-be88-e1510e226f89.png\" width=\"75\" height=\"75\" alt=\"CurseForge\">\n      </a>\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n\n<!-- Small divider (centered) | BANNER #1 -->\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1283693/description_24a4c720-e0b7-4b40-876b-fdbb5091f1f0.png\" width=\"850\" alt=\"\">\n</p>\n\n***\n\n<!-- YOUR ORIGINAL WRITING (kept) -->\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>First Person Model </strong>and <strong>Alien Evolution</strong> are two amazing mods, but they were heavily incompatible with each other. When using them together, players faced major issues:</span>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Looking down would completely cover the screen depending on the alien's model</span></li>\n  <li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Many aliens with unique body shapes made the first-person rendering view completely unusable<span style=\"color: #236fa1;\"><br></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">\n    <span style=\"color: #72a41c;\"><strong>Alien Evolution: First-Person Model</strong></span><br>\n    This mod is a compatibility bridge designed to make these two fantastic mods work together. It automatically detects your alien transformation and adjusts the camera accordingly, giving you a proper first-person experience for every alien form.\n  </span>\n</blockquote>\n\n***\n\n<!-- Small divider (centered) placed AFTER the line below the sentence | BANNER #2 -->\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1283693/description_24a4c720-e0b7-4b40-876b-fdbb5091f1f0.png\" width=\"850\" alt=\"\">\n</p>\n\n<!-- ⬆️ No horizontal line here anymore. Goes straight to images. -->\n\n<!-- Showcase images: centered -->\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1283693/description_ffa78d4d-d251-4fdc-abe7-36a16ebd2079.png\" width=\"850\" alt=\"\"><br><br>\n  <img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1283693/description_788fb16b-49a8-4332-9b20-badfffa13a5f.png\" width=\"850\" alt=\"\"><br><br>\n  <img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1283693/description_5232bd6f-be5c-4dcb-9269-80efa4ea6186.png\" width=\"850\" alt=\"\">\n</p>\n\n<!-- Small divider (centered) | BANNER #3 -->\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1283693/description_24a4c720-e0b7-4b40-876b-fdbb5091f1f0.png\" width=\"850\" alt=\"\">\n</p>\n\n<!-- Early dev note (kept) -->\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><strong><br>EARLY DEVELOPMENT WARNING:</strong></span> This mod is still in heavy development. While it makes the mods playable together, some features may not work perfectly (or at all) yet.</span>\n",
